r~ [options] [<dir>]
r~ --help
r~ --Version

<dir> defaults to .
--verbose only opt currently supported.

r~
r~ .
r~ <dir>

r~ [-v | --verbose] [-r | --recursive] [<dir>]

r~ -h | --help

r~ -V | --Version

opts:
  -v --verbose   // synonym for --verbosity=2
  -y --verbosity // int in 0,1,2,3 <=> silent,normal,verbose,debug
  -r --recursive
  -c --continue-on-error

If both --verbose and --verbosity are supplied, then verbosity must be 2.
